00:00:07,998 --> 00:00:10,064
No! Rainbow Dash!

6
00:00:10,583 --> 00:00:11,361
<i>(growl)</i>

7
00:00:11,596 --> 00:00:13,449
How in Equestria does
that pony expect to pass

8
00:00:13,455 --> 00:00:15,125
her History of the
Wonderbolts exam tomorrow

9
00:00:15,133 --> 00:00:16,702
if she's wasting time flying?

10
00:00:18,119 --> 00:00:19,537
I'm just gonna fly
right up to her

11
00:00:19,549 --> 00:00:20,366
and tell her what I think

12
00:00:20,370 --> 00:00:22,476
about her lackadaisical
approach to studying.

13
00:00:22,747 --> 00:00:24,095
Won't she be surprised.

14
00:00:24,126 --> 00:00:24,735
Surprise!

15
00:00:24,780 --> 00:00:26,618
What? Huh?
How did you?

16
00:00:26,739 --> 00:00:28,146
Please, Twilight.

17
00:00:28,353 --> 00:00:30,230
That was the worst
sneak attack ever.

18
00:00:31,871 --> 00:00:32,565
What? But--

19
00:00:32,667 --> 00:00:34,967
I saw you giving me the
stink eye from the ground.

20
00:00:35,135 --> 00:00:38,095
And heard you flying towards me
and muttering from a mile away.

21
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:40,507
Well, if you heard me
muttering then you must know

22
00:00:40,515 --> 00:00:41,705
what I was muttering about.

23
00:00:41,988 --> 00:00:44,405
Yeah, yeah, the
Wonderbolts History test.

24
00:00:44,684 --> 00:00:45,730
No big deal.

25
00:00:47,631 --> 00:00:48,868
No. Big Deal.

26
00:00:49,079 --> 00:00:50,009
Really Big
Deal.

27
00:00:50,078 --> 00:00:50,883
It's a test!

28
00:00:51,047 --> 00:00:52,612
A test that will
determine if you can join

29
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:54,468
the newly formed
Wonderbolts Reserves.

30
00:00:54,706 --> 00:00:56,275
And being part of the
Wonderbolts Reserves

31
00:00:56,282 --> 00:00:57,309
means you'll have
the opportunity

32
00:00:57,311 --> 00:00:58,864
to live your dream
as a Wonderbolt.

33
00:00:59,090 --> 00:01:01,490
This is the most important
test of your life!

34
00:01:01,701 --> 00:01:04,440
Twilight, not everypony
gets all freaked out

35
00:01:04,450 --> 00:01:05,748
about tests like you.

36
00:01:06,142 --> 00:01:08,956
I do not get all
freaked out about tests.

37
00:01:09,504 --> 00:01:10,762
Uh, seriously?

38
00:01:11,334 --> 00:01:14,546
Your freak-outs are so epic you
sing whole "freak-out" arias

39
00:01:14,552 --> 00:01:15,440
about freaking out.

40
00:01:16,150 --> 00:01:19,652
Fine. I may tend to take my
tests a little seriously.

41
00:01:20,105 --> 00:01:22,790
But that doesn't mean you
shouldn't be studying for yours.

42
00:01:24,224 --> 00:01:27,235
Oooh! And I know just the
pony who can help you!

43
00:01:27,301 --> 00:01:27,925
<i>(slap)</i>

44
00:01:29,114 --> 00:01:29,812
Me!

45
00:01:30,050 --> 00:01:32,023
This is going to
so much fun!

46
00:01:32,146 --> 00:01:32,569
(pow!)

47
00:01:32,747 --> 00:01:33,676
(pow!)

48
00:01:35,611 --> 00:01:37,531
Sure. Fun.

