Well, I give it a
"Whoa, whoa, what?"

244
00:10:11,186 --> 00:10:14,312
I'm totally confused and
I just want to go home.

245
00:10:14,378 --> 00:10:15,765
Whoa! Hey!

246
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:17,680
Whoa, your woes,
there Woeful.

