00:10:24,577 --> 00:10:25,141
<i>♪ (rap beat) </i>

250
00:10:25,174 --> 00:10:26,401
Boom, boom, che.

251
00:10:26,478 --> 00:10:29,399
Boom, boom, boom, che.

